 Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in final farewells and preparations for the descent."},{"name":"Marina","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Ares","description":"Member of the Phobos team staying on Ares to guide the lander.","relationships":[{"character":"Raul","relationship":"Partner"},{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in final farewells and preparations for the descent."},{"name":"Alex Zhalin","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Ares","description":"Crew member involved in sexual rumors","relationships":[{"character":"Janet Blyleven","relationship":"Romantic rival"},{"character":"Mary Dunkel","relationship":"Romantic rival"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in sexual gossip, engaged in public relationship dynamics"},{"name":"Tatiana","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Ares","description":"Member of the Phobos team staying on Ares to guide the lander.","relationships":[{"character":"Arkady Bogdanov","relationship":"Group member"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in final farewells and preparations for the descent."},{"name":"Yeli Zudov","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Ares","description":"A crew member present during Maya's bathroom scene.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Mentioned in the context of Maya's interactions with other crew members."},{"name":"Roger","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Member of the Phobos team staying on Ares to guide the lander.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Resumed work at base, accompanied Arkady Bogdanov from Phobos."},{"name":"Simon Frazier","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"4","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Quiet ally of 