ern biases."},{"name":"Nejm","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1","currentLocation":"Nicosia","description":"An Arab involved in discussions about Mars' political future and John Boone's influence.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Participated in conversations about John Boone's policies and the future of Mars settlements."},{"name":"Selim el-Hayil","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1","currentLocation":"Nicosia","description":"A young Arab with strong opinions about John Boone's policies and the future of Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Strategic ally"}],"recentEvents":"Engaged in a tense conversation with Frank Chalmers about John Boone's potential actions and the fate of Arab settlements."},{"name":"Michel Duval","aliases":["Michel"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Psychiatrist sent to observe and evaluate candidates for the Mars colony, noting the psychological stresses of the selection process.","relationships":[{"character":"Charles York","relationship":"Chairman of the psychiatrists' committee, debated selection criteria with Michel"},{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague in mission planning"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Arkady Bogdanov","relationship":"Debated psychological testing methodologies"},{"character":"Phyllis Boyle","relationship":"Reassured her about mission challenges"},{"character":"Nadia","relationship":"Psychological care provider"},{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in the areophany initiation ceremony, accepted invitation to join the group"},{"name":"Charles York","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Antarctica","description":"Chairman of the psychiatrists' committee, engaged in discussions about the selection proces