"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Antarctica","description":"Chairman of the psychiatrists' committee, engaged in discussions about the selection process for Mars colonists.","relationships":[{"character":"Michel Duval","relationship":"Debated selection criteria with Michel"}],"recentEvents":"Engaged in dialogue with Michel Duval about the challenges of evaluating candidates for the Mars mission."},{"name":"Arkady Bogdanov","aliases":["Arkady"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"9","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"A key figure in the Mars colonization project, known for his radical ideas about terraforming.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague in mission dynamics"},{"character":"Nadia","relationship":"Collaborator on construction projects"},{"character":"Phyllis Boyle","relationship":"Frequent antagonist"},{"character":"Nadia Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"opponent in terraforming debates"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Close friend"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in reunion and sabotage discussions"},{"name":"Nadia Cherneshevsky","aliases":["Nadezhda Francine Cherneshevsky","Nadezhda Cherneshevsky","Nadia"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"9","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"A key figure in the colony's construction efforts, known for her work on the permanent habitat and her role as a mediator in interpersonal conflicts.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Friend and occasional confidante"},{"character":"Arkady Bogdanov","relationship":"Close collaborator and frequent argumentative partner"},{"character":"Ann Clayborne","relationship":"Colleague and frequent debate partner on geological theories"},{"character":"Sax Russell","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Vlad Taneev","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Close friend"},{"c