olt, discussed its challenges, and was part of the rover group."},{"name":"Yeli Zudov","aliases":["Yeli"],"importance":"main","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Resident of Lasswitz, participated in aquifer containment efforts.","relationships":[{"character":"Nadia Cherneshevsky","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Sasha Yefremov","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Last seen in Cairo; presumed missing after the chaos"},{"name":"Roger","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Member of the Phobos team staying on Ares to guide the lander.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Resumed work at base, accompanied Arkady Bogdanov from Phobos."},{"name":"Simon Frazier","aliases":["Simon"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Valles Marineris canyon bottom","description":"A colonist involved in the political and social structures of the Martian settlement.","relationships":[{"character":"Ann Clayborne","relationship":"Colleague and fellow colonist"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague and fellow colonist"},{"character":"Nadia Cherneshevsky","relationship":"Traveler group member"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the group after being greeted by the young driver at the canyon entrance"},{"name":"Gene","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"9","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Brickmaker struggling with production quality and material composition.","relationships":[{"character":"Nadia","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Close friend"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in reunion and sabotage discussions"},{"name":"Igor","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"2","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"Team member involved in parachute salvage and geological surveys.","relation