se and farm development"},{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Involved in a complex relationship dynamic with Maya"},{"character":"Simon Frazier","relationship":"Team member"},{"character":"Michel Duval","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Tatiana Durova","relationship":"Friend (deceased)"},{"character":"Yeli Zudov","relationship":"Partner in rebuilding efforts"},{"character":"Sasha Yefremov","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Helped Maya and managed medical concerns during the journey."},{"name":"Vlad Taneev","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Acheron","description":"Nobel Prize-winning medical biologist, part of the Russian contingent.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague in mission planning"},{"character":"Ursula Kohl","relationship":"Partner"}],"recentEvents":"Traveled to Acheron to avoid tuberculosis outbreak in Elysium"},{"name":"Hiroko Ai","aliases":["Hiroko"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"3","currentLocation":"Polar cap village","description":"A key figure in the Martian colonization efforts, known for her reproductive contributions to the project.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Competing for influence in Martian governance"},{"character":"Rya Jimenez","relationship":"Collaborated on tunneljump game"},{"character":"Arkady Bogdanov","relationship":"Unconfirmed alliance"},{"character":"Nadia","relationship":"Collaborator on farm projects"},{"character":"Sax Russell","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Michel Duval","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Longtime friend, estranged for 20 years"},{"character":"Kasei","relationship":"Parent of child involved in sabotage activities"}],"recentEvents":"Welcomed the group to the polar cap village"},{"name":"Ivana","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1","currentLocation":"Nicosia","descriptio